==English==
==Pronunciation==
mi·cro-re·gion

=== Etymology ===
[[micro-]] and [[region]]

=== Noun ===
#A administrative system that is equivalent to a [[county]] or a [[prefecture]] and a [[department]].  It is used in [[Brazil]] as a fourth-level administration after [[macro-region]] and [[municipalities]].

